title: Fort Bend Co. health officials confirm first case of measles in area linked to international travel
body: The Fort Bend County Health and Human Services confirmed its first case of measles in the county on Sunday. According to a press release, the case involves a 50- to 60-year-old woman who was potentially exposed after recently traveling internationally.
